{"tid":2292180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[VIUTV]原來個Judas Law唱歌咁撚難聽, 仲話開過演唱會X_X","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T07:19:22.000Z","uid":67294,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc7f82645bd656f53eb06fb5ba51f64e0c5c330","tid":2292180,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JOPXrK4uPKY&amp;ab_channel=ViuTV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJOPXrK4uPKY%26ab_channel%3DViuTV&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=d94cb0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JOPXrK4uPKY&amp;ab_channel=ViuTV</a><br />\n<br />\n一上高音就無哂力, 落低音又唔穩, 呼吸又唔順唱到扯蝦咁<br />\n支結他彈左幾多年都剩係識掃chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都質素都話開過演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想講全民造星班人點解唱歌咁難聽都過到初選, 認真係啲大專星con是但執一個都唔會唱得差過佢地啦<br />\n人地台灣聲林之王海選清唱就算過唔到果班都好過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MNY7ftPMuGs&amp;ab_channel=%E8%81%B2%E6%9E%97%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8BJungleVoice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMNY7ftPMuGs%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%259E%2597%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%258E%258BJungleVoice&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=59cc187c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MNY7ftPMuGs&amp;ab_channel=%E8%81%B2%E6%9E%97%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8BJungleVoice</a>"},{"pid":"779a7ec5be7a7018b76dab7475dcca80640a2f48","tid":2292180,"uid":4811,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"以前都唔覺得佢唱歌特別好聽，唔知點解啲人煲大佢"},{"pid":"136063a2d9cb017dc3ae28969573e502681b9700","tid":2292180,"uid":70988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"p